dc_creator_sm: Community Development Agency, County of Marin, California
dc_description_s: A sphere of influence is a plan adopted by LAFCO for the probable physical boundaries and service areas of a city or special district.  Water District Sphere of Influence is a topologically correct polygon representation of sphere of influence boundaries of the water districts of Marin County.
dc_publisher_s: San Rafael (Calif.). County Of Marin Community Development Agency.
dc_title_s: Marin County Water District Sphere of Influence
